data-triple-N3.o: "Marshall Bruce Mathers III (born October 17, 1972), better known by his stage name Eminem (stylized as EMINEM) and by his alter ego Slim Shady, is an American rapper, record producer, songwriter and actor. Eminem, along with his solo career, is a member of his group D12, and also one half of the hip hop duo Bad Meets Evil, with Royce da 5'9". Eminem is one of the best-selling artists in the world and is the best-selling artist of the 2000s."@en
